      "properties": {"Node name for S&R": "Note"},
      "widgets_values": [
        "LTX-VIDEO SCENE RENDERER (LTX 2.3 / 0.9.1)\n========================================\n\nUSE THIS WORKFLOW FOR: fast prototyping, scene iteration, motion tests\nEXPECTED SPEED: ~30-45s per 5s clip at 512x512 on 4090 mobile (16GB)\n\nWIDGET NOTES:\n- widgets_values[0..3] on LTXImageToVideo = width, height, length, batch_size\n  (length 97 frames @ 24fps ≈ 4 seconds)\n- widgets_values[4] = context_schedule (0.7 = balanced motion)\n- widgets_values[5] = steps (25-30 for quality)\n- widgets_values[6] = cfg (3.0-4.0 typical; lower = more motion, higher = more faithful to ref)\n- widgets_values[7] = sampler_sigma_shift (1.0 default)\n- widgets_values[8] = schedule (fixed / exponential / noise)\n- widgets_values[9] = stp (faster / fast / normal)\n- widgets_values[10] = seed (fixed for reproducibility)\n\nFOR 16GB VRAM:\n  512x512x97 frames  → ~9GB peak, safe\n  768x432x97 frames  → ~13GB peak, OK\n  1024x576x97 frames → ~17GB, will OOM. Use Wan 1.3B or downscale.\n\nOVERDRIVE TO WAN:\n  When you find a shot you like, re-render with workflows/02_scene_render_Wan.json\n  for sharper photoreal output."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
